---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="The Experiment"
  description="How the CAL DMRadio experiment works: solenoidal LC resonator, SQUID amplifiers, and quantum-limited axion searches."
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">CAL DMRadio</span>
      <h1>The Experiment</h1>
      <p class="desc">
        [One-sentence summary of the CAL experiment for the page header]
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col-60">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Overview</span>
          <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">How DMRadio Works</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            [How CAL converts an axion signal into a measurable current — describe the magnet, pickup coil, and axion-photon conversion mechanism]
          </p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            [How the LC resonator enhances the signal, what quality factor means, and how tuning scans across different axion masses]
          </p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            [How the SQUID amplifier chain reads out the signal and why millikelvin temperatures are needed for quantum-limited noise]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
          <div class="diagram-placeholder">
            <p><strong>Detector schematic</strong></p>
            <p>Coaxial pickup coil + SQUID chain</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Key Parameters</h4>
            <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.875rem;">
              <tr><td style="padding:0.3rem 0;color:var(--gray-500);">Mass range</td><td style="color:var(--gray-900);font-weight:500;">[X &ndash; Y] &mu;eV</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:0.3rem 0;color:var(--gray-500);">Frequency</td><td style="color:var(--gray-900);font-weight:500;">[X &ndash; Y] MHz</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:0.3rem 0;color:var(--gray-500);">Temperature</td><td style="color:var(--gray-900);font-weight:500;">[X] mK</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:0.3rem 0;color:var(--gray-500);">Magnetic field</td><td style="color:var(--gray-900);font-weight:500;">[X] T</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:0.3rem 0;color:var(--gray-500);">Noise level</td><td style="color:var(--gray-900);font-weight:500;">Near SQL</td></tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider">

  <!-- What it searches for -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Science Target</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">What We Search For</h2>
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">QCD Axions</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            [Why axions are a compelling dark matter candidate — the strong CP problem and Peccei-Quinn symmetry]
          </p>
          <p>
            [What axion mass range CAL targets and why that range is physically motivated]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Dark Photons & ALPs</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            [Description of axion-like particles and dark photons as additional search targets]
          </p>
          <p>
            [CAL's sensitivity projections across the ALP and dark photon parameter space]
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider">

  <!-- Setup / hardware -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Hardware</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Detector Setup</h2>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">Coaxial Resonator</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the pickup coil geometry and the LC circuit]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">SQUID Amplifiers</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the SQUID amplifier chain and how it achieves quantum-limited noise]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">Cryogenic System</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the dilution refrigerator and operating temperature]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">Magnet</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the superconducting magnet: field strength and how it drives axion-photon conversion]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">Data Acquisition</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the data acquisition chain and how axion signals are identified above the noise floor]
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--blue);">Analysis Pipeline</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;">
            [Description of the analysis pipeline for identifying candidates and setting exclusion limits]
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="background:var(--gray-50);border-top:1px solid var(--gray-200);">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Want to learn more?</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;max-width:500px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        [Short invitation for visitors to read publications or get in touch]
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href={`${base}/publications/`} class="btn btn-primary">Publications</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
